reviewText: Found this at the library and checked it out for the heck of it. Information seemed useful, but couldn't watch for long - corny script, not-so-great (sometimes ham) acting (and terrible foreign accent imitations always rub me the wrong way). Since this is marked "High school grade level" - I didn't notice that right away - I wonder if high schoolers would actually sit through this and learn somethingor if they, too, would roll their eyes and bail.
